import { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis } from 'recharts'
const data = [
    { name: '11/2020', uv: 400, pv: 2400, amt: 2400 },
    { name: '12/2020', uv: 400, pv: 2400, amt: 2400 },
    { name: '01/2021', uv: 400, pv: 2400, amt: 2400 },
    { name: '02/2021', uv: 300, pv: 3400, amt: 3400 },
    { name: '03/2021', uv: 300, pv: 3400, amt: 3400 },
    { name: '04/2021', uv: 300, pv: 3400, amt: 3400 },
]

export default function Rechart() {
    return (
        <LineChart width={400} height={400} data={data}>
            <Line type="monotone" dataKey="uv" stroke="#8884d8" />
            <XAxis dataKey="name" />
            <YAxis />
        </LineChart>
    )
}
